					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12085842#post-4283590</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12085842/scp-4211#post-4283590</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2019 17:47:28 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Ayers</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1856789</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The entries do change slightly with different selections just to fit the prompt a little better. It's nothing major since I wanted to keep the narrative the same through all the iterations.</p> <p>I <em>did</em> want to make this a proper CYOA, but I figured that'd make it almost exponentially harder to write and code. So, as it stands, each version only changes the flow a little; the destination's the same, but how you get there is tailored to your choices.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
